The '''xUSSR Railway Set''' includes locomotives, DMUs, EMUs and other rolling stock from the former [http://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian Empire Russian Empire], [http://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soviet Union Soviet Union], the [http://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commonwealth_of_Independent_States CIS] and several countries contained within the former USSR. All vehicles are drawn in realistic extended scale, exceeding original Transport Tycoon graphics. All technical features such as power, tractive effort, capacity, production date etc. are based on pecularities and functionality of real vehicles.


